snippet.title: The List
snippet.description: The List is a women’s news and lifestyle destination with a twist. From reality TV to Hollywood and everything in-between, we’ve got you covered. We obsess over tried-and-true beauty hacks and all things royal family. And we’ll keep you up to date on news and politics, too, from who’s making headlines to how those headlines affect you. The List has what you need, whether it’s real-life news or a break from it.
